    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      138.38,
      531.0,
      150.38
    ],
    "text": "The land forming the subject matter of this application is state land within the meaning of the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      160.34,
      538.24,
      172.34
    ],
    "text": "Land Development Ordinance No. 19 of 1935 as amended (Land Development Ordinance). One",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      179.75,
      538.04,
      194.3
    ],
    "text": "David Appuhamy, father of the original 6th Respondent, was granted a permit for this land (P3).",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      204.26,
      267.24,
      216.26
    ],
    "text": "David Appuhamy passed away in 1991.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      236.3,
      542.32,
      248.3
    ],
    "text": "David Appuhamy had two brothers namely Sugathan Appuhamy and Wijeris Appuhamy, the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      258.29,
      542.45,
      270.29
    ],
    "text": "grandfather of the Petitioner. Initially David Appuhamy had nominated Sugathan Appuhamy as",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      280.25,
      542.34,
      292.25
    ],
    "text": "his successor. At the time this nomination was made David Appuhamy was unmarried. Later",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      302.21,
      542.28,
      314.21
    ],
    "text": "upon his marriage the nomination of Sugathan Appuhamy became null and void in terms of",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      324.17,
      323.76,
      336.17
    ],
    "text": "section 52(1) of the Land Development Ordinance.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      356.09,
      542.47,
      368.09
    ],
    "text": "There is no dispute between the parties that David Appuhamy did not nominate a successor.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      378.17,
      542.28,
      390.17
    ],
    "text": "Hence upon his death, succession must take place in terms of section 72 of the Land",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      397.58,
      338.06,
      412.13
    ],
    "text": "Development Ordinance and the 3rd Schedule therein.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      432.07,
      542.6,
      444.07
    ],
    "text": "However, the Petitioner claims that the land in issue was cultivated by his grandfather and his",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      454.03,
      542.65,
      466.03
    ],
    "text": "two brothers although the permit was issued to David Appuhamy. It is further claimed that",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      475.99,
      542.4,
      487.99
    ],
    "text": "David Appuhamy left this land and settled down in Nochchiyagama in 1945 with his partner and",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      497.95,
      542.37,
      509.95
    ],
    "text": "he was later granted lands in Nochchiyagama under the Mahaweli project. The Petitioner",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      520.03,
      542.28,
      532.03
    ],
    "text": "asserts that after David Appuhamy and Sugathan Appuhamy left the land, it was his grandfather",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      541.99,
      542.8,
      553.99
    ],
    "text": "Wijeris Appuhamy who solely possessed and cultivated it. Wijeris Appuhamy died in 1995 while",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      563.95,
      534.41,
      575.95
    ],
    "text": "his wife died in 2008. They had three sons and a daughter who is the mother of the Petitioner.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      595.9,
      542.22,
      607.9
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner contends that from the time of the death of his grandfather in 1995, he was",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      617.86,
      542.59,
      629.86
    ],
    "text": "cultivating this land. According to him, his father started building a house on the land in 2009",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      639.82,
      542.28,
      651.82
    ],
    "text": "which was halted in the same year due to financial constraints. The construction resumed in",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      661.9,
      284.4,
      673.9
    ],
    "text": "2014 and was completed by January 2016.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      731.26,
      542.6,
      755.74
    ],
    "text": "Page 4 of 7",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri",
      "Calibri,Bold"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      11.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      71.85,
      542.7,
      86.42
    ],
    "text": "Somewhere in September 2015, the Petitioner made a request to the 4th Respondent to grant",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      96.38,
      542.36,
      108.38
    ],
    "text": "the land in issue to him. Around October 2017 the Petitioner was made aware that the original",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      115.79,
      346.7,
      130.34
    ],
    "text": "permit (P3) has been transferred to the 6th Respondent.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      147.83,
      542.81,
      162.38
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner in this application is seeking to challenge the actions or inactions of the 1st to 5th",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      172.34,
      542.3,
      184.34
    ],
    "text": "Respondents which resulted in the failure to issue a permit or grant to the Petitioner in terms of",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      194.3,
      542.33,
      206.3
    ],
    "text": "the Land Development Ordinance in respect of the land which the Petitioner and his",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      216.26,
      542.73,
      228.26
    ],
    "text": "predecessors were occupying and cultivating from 1937 and the illegal transfer of the permit",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      235.67,
      209.28,
      250.22
    ],
    "text": "(P3) to the 6th Respondent.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.039999961853027,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      270.29,
      542.33,
      282.29
    ],
    "text": "While all parties have filed extensive and undoubtedly helpful written submissions raising many",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      292.25,
      542.3,
      304.25
    ],
    "text": "interesting points of law, in my view Court must first examine whether the Petitioner has come",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      314.21,
      542.67,
      326.21
    ],
    "text": "to Court with clean hands in that he has not suppressed and/or misrepresented material facts",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      336.17,
      120.81,
      348.17
    ],
    "text": "to Court.",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      368.09,
      354.02,
      380.09
    ],
    "text": "Suppression and/or Misrepresentation of Material Facts",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri,BoldItalic"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      404.09,
      542.3,
      416.09
    ],
    "text": "It is established law that discretionary relief will be refused by Court without going into the",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      426.07,
      542.69,
      438.07
    ],
    "text": "merits if there has been suppression and/or misrepresentation of material facts. It is necessary",
    "fonts": [
      "Calibri"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
